索赔报告称 Gen Con 2023 小偷偷走了价值 236,000 英镑的 TCG 卡https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/gen-con-2023-thieves-stole-236000-worth-of-tcg-cards-claims-report-3479267?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=gen- con-2023-thieves-stole-236000-worth-of-tcg-cards-claims-reportImogen Donovan Mon, 07 Aug 2023 11:46:12 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsTabletop Gaming https://www.nme.com/?p=3479267 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trading-cards-stolen-in-indianapolis.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trading-cards-stolen-in-indianapolis.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trading-cards-stolen-in-indianapolis-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trading-cards-stolen-in-indianapolis-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trading-cards-stolen-in-indianapolis-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trading-cards-stolen-in-indianapolis-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trading-cards-stolen-in-indianapolis-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>警方呼吁任何有信息的人与我们联系</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/gen-con-2023-thieves-stole-236000-worth-of-tcg-cards-claims-report-3479267">2023 年 Gen Con 大会后，窃贼偷走了价值 236,000 英镑的 TCG 卡，索赔报告</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trading-cards-stolen-in-indianapolis.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trading-cards-stolen-in-indianapolis.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trading-cards-stolen-in-indianapolis-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trading-cards-stolen-in-indianapolis-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trading-cards-stolen-in-indianapolis-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trading-cards-stolen-in-indianapolis-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trading-cards-stolen-in-indianapolis-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据称，价值约 300,000 美元（236,000 英镑）的集换式纸牌游戏卡在印第安纳波利斯被盗，图像显示嫌疑人拿走了一个装满盒子的托盘。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/theres-never-been-a-better-time-to-be-a-warhammer-fan-3447946">现在是成为“战锤”粉丝的最佳时机</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://local.nixle.com/alert/10248167/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">印第安纳波利斯市警察局</a>(IMPD) 称，这起事件发生在 8 月 2 日，即在印第安纳会议中心举办的 Gen Con 2023 开幕前一天。该活动是北美同类活动中规模最大的一次，旨在宣传该地区的“<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/tabletop-gaming">桌面游戏</a>之乡”。</p><p> “据报道，感兴趣的人购买了一台托盘搬运车，移走了一托盘游戏卡，并将它们转移到了一个未知的位置，”IMPD 呼吁任何知情者提供有关抢劫的信息或图像中人员的身份。取得了联系。</p><p>声明称：“这起盗窃案发生在市中心活动开始之前，当时商贩们正在不同时间摆设展示品。”</p><p> Ravensburger 对<a href="https://www.dicebreaker.com/events/gen-con-2023/news/gen-con-2023-card-theft" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Dicebreaker</em>的报告</a>做出回应，确认窃贼并未获得任何<em>Lorcana</em>股票。在 Gen Con 2023 上，粉丝们<a href="https://gizmodo.com/lorcana-gen-con-line-tcg-disney-trading-card-game-1850707898" target="_blank" rel="noopener">等待了数十个小时</a>才能购买迪士尼新集换式卡牌游戏的卡牌。领取预发行卡的队伍显然从市中心蔓延到了街道上。 </p><figure id="attachment_3479285" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3479285" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3479285" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/disney-lorcana-artwork-mickey.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/disney-lorcana-artwork-mickey.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/disney-lorcana-artwork-mickey-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-