 1975在马来西亚引发争议后面临法律诉讼https://www.nme.com/news/music/good-vibes-festival-pursue-legal-action-over-matty-healy-the-1975-set-3479272?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=good-vibes-节日对马蒂希利 1975 年集采取法律行动Liberty DunworthMon, 07 Aug 2023 10:43:08 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3479272 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/the-1975-matty-healy-2023.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="1975 年马蒂·希利" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/the-1975-matty-healy-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/the-1975-matty-healy-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/the-1975-matty-healy-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/the-1975-matty-healy-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/the-1975-matty-healy-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/the-1975-matty-healy-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该乐队因批评政府的反 LGBTQ 法律而被禁止进入该国。</p><p> 《The 1975》在马来西亚备受争议的设定首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/good-vibes-festival-pursue-legal-action-over-matty-healy-the-1975-set-3479272">后面临法律诉讼</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/the-1975-matty-healy-2023.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="1975 年马蒂·希利" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/the-1975-matty-healy-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/the-1975-matty-healy-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/the-1975-matty-healy-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/the-1975-matty-healy-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/the-1975-matty-healy-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/the-1975-matty-healy-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Good Vibes Festival 的组织者宣布，他们将对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">The 1975</a>采取法律行动，因为该乐队利用他们的乐队批评马来西亚的反 LGBTQ 法律。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-1975-live-in-london-setlist-photos-3464005">1975 年伦敦现场演出：网络狂热中的庆祝活动</a></strong></li></ul><p>这一时刻发生在 7 月 21 日——为期三天的音乐节的第一天——乐队的头条新闻中，主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matty-healy">马蒂·希利 (Matty Healy)</a>在舞台上喝酒时，砸碎了音乐节运营的无人机，并在人群面前亲吻了贝斯手罗斯·麦克唐纳 (Ross MacDonald)。</p><p>演出被缩短，第二天，为期三天的音乐节的剩余时间被当局取消，希利和乐队都<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-banned-from-malaysia-good-vibes-festival-cancelled-matty-healy-3471893">被禁止在该国演出</a>。</p><p>现在，已证实音乐节背后的组织者——Future Sound Asia——正在对他们采取法律行动，并向这支英国独立乐队发出了一份索赔信。</p><p>根据新闻稿，索赔要求 The 1975 承认其责任并赔偿 Future Sound Asia (FSA) 所遭受的损失。它还指出，如果乐队不这样做，组织者将向英格兰法院提起法律诉讼。</p><p> “FSA 想要重申他们对乐队在 GVF2023 演出期间的行为的强烈不满，”它写道。 “特别是主唱马修·蒂莫西·希利的辱骂性语言、损坏设备和不雅的舞台行为，不仅公然违反了当地准则和马来西亚法律，也玷污了这个已有10年历史的音乐节的声誉。” </p><figure id="attachment_3471896" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3471896" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3471896" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty.jpg" alt="1975年" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/matty-healy-the-1975-live-2023-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3471896" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年 6 月，马蒂·希利 (Matty Healy) 与 The 1975 一起现场表演。图片来源：Thomas Niedermueller/Getty Images。</figcaption></figure><p>索赔信除了指出舞台上的表演“玷污”了电影节的声誉外，还指出他们的行为“故意违反了与 FSA 达成的协议”，并直接导致 2023 年电影节被取消。</p><p>它补充说，这导致“FSA 遭受重大财务损失，并对依赖音乐节成功的当地艺术家和企业产生负面影响，影响了许多马来西亚人的生计。”</p><p> The 1975 的代表告诉<em>NME</em> ，他们目前不予置评。</p><p>继上个月登上头条新闻后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/malaysian-lgbtq-community-condemn-the-1975s-matty-healy-over-kiss-incident-3472210">马来西亚 LGBTQ+ 群体谴责了希利</a>，并表示希利的行为将使该国 LGBTQ+ 群体的生活变得更糟。</p><p>音乐节结束后一周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/muse">Muse</a>成为自经历磨难以来第一支在吉隆坡演出的国际艺人，据透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/muse-remove-song-malaysia-concert-setlist-the-1975-controversy-3474127">乐队从歌单中删除了一首歌曲，以更好地适应该国的表演准则</a>。乐队没有演奏“We Are Fucking Fucked”，而是演奏了“Resistance”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blink-182">Blink-182</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-delonge">Tom DeLonge</a>也对此事发表了看法，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blink-182-tom-delonge-not-going-to-malaysia-matty-healy-the-1975-kiss-lollapalooza-3479130">表示他在芝加哥 Lollapalooza 与 Healy 接吻后不会前往马来西亚</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3478627" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3478627" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3478627" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-1975-Josh-BrastedFilmMagic.jpg" alt="1975年" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-1975-Josh-BrastedFilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-1975-Josh-BrastedFilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-1975-Josh-BrastedFilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-1975-Josh-BrastedFilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-1975-Josh-BrastedFilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-1975-Josh-BrastedFilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3478627" class="wp-caption-text"> 1975 年片尾字幕：Josh Brasted / FilmMagic</figcaption></figure><p>他在 Instagram 上分享了他和马蒂·希利在中场拥抱的屏幕截图。 “我想我自己‘和’The 1975 不会去马来西亚——只是几个家伙在 Lollapalooza 的精彩演出中接吻，”他写道。</p><p>在 Lollapalooza 的其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-matty-healy-seems-to-poke-fun-at-malaysian-controversy-during-lollapalooza-3478526">The 1975 在表演“It&#39;s Not Living If It&#39;s Not With You”之前似乎取笑了马来西亚的争议</a>。</p><p>在他们的演出中，希利开始说了一些有争议的话，然后乐队突然用歌曲的开头即兴重复段打断了他。在今年的 Lollapalooza 音乐节上表演这首歌时，希利说道：“你想要我的旅行小费吗？不要去……”，然后就被赛道的起点打断了。</p><p> 《The 1975》在马来西亚备受争议的设定首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/good-vibes-festival-pursue-legal-action-over-matty-healy-the-1975-set-3479272">后面临法律诉讼</a>。</p> ;
